  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="41263926">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/120741578/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u120741578-6.jpg" alt="Travis1997" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/41263926/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/41263926/" class="">第383页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/120741578/" class=" " title="Travis1997">Travis1997</a>
                (一線斷時，落落磊磊。)
              
                <span class="allstar20" title="较差"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="41263926">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">作為明代中後期“練兵”運動成果的受惠者，清朝軍隊在相當長的時期內保持着強大的戰鬥能力。
李斌，西式武器對清初作戰方法的影響</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-01-15 03:21</span>
                  
